'''飓风邦尼'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Bonnie}}）是[[1992年大西洋飓风季|1992年大西洋飓风季]]中一场持续时间很长的风暴，也是该季第三场[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]（包括四月的亚热带风暴）和第二场飓风<ref name="Unisys">{{cite web | author = Unisys Weather | year = 1992 | title = Unisys Weather: 1992 Hurricane/Tropical Data for Atlantic | publisher = Unisys | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160409031711/http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/atlantic/1992/index.html | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2016-10-16 | url = http://weather.unisys.com/hurricane/atlantic/1992/index.html | archivedate = 2016-04-09 }}</ref>。气旋于9月17日在中大西洋高[[纬度|纬度]]海域成型，之后存在的大部分时间里都没有遇到足够强度的转向气流，所以有一个多星期几乎没有移动。9月27日，飓风开始缓慢向东面和东北方向的[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]前进。9月30日，风暴在转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]前短暂对该群岛构成影响，但没有报导表明当地因此遭受破坏。

== 气象历史 ==
{{Storm path|Bonnie 1992 track.png}}
9月11日，一股[[冷锋|冷锋]]逐渐离开[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]进入大西洋。冷锋进入[[亚热带|亚热带]]海域，于9月15日在[[百慕大|百慕大]]以东不远处停止前进。接下来两天里，云层逐渐同冷锋分离并凝聚成[[低气压|低气压区]]。<ref name="BonnieTCR1">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | date = 1992-12-01 | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Bonnie 17-30 September 1992 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-16 | page = 1 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233847/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992-prelim/bonnie/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992-prelim/bonnie/prelim01.gif | deadurl = no | format = [[GIF|GIF]] }}</ref>9月17日下午，这片天气系统已经充分组织，成为第四号热带低气压<ref name="Bonnie1">{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | date = 1992-09-17 | title = Tropical Depression Four Discussion Number 1 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-16 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.001 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303195210/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.001 }}</ref>。

9月17日夜间到次日早上，气旋稳步组织。9月18日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]把开始缓慢朝东北方向移动的热带低气压升级成热带风暴，并以“邦尼”（{{lang|en|Bonnie}}）命名。<ref name="Bonnie4">{{cite report | author = Edward N. Rappaport | date = 1992-09-18 | title = Tropical Storm Bonnie Discussion Number 4 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200045/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.004 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-16 | format = TXT | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.004 }}</ref>。像大部分在高纬度发展的风暴一样，邦尼起初也同大范围气旋式环流结合在一起，这样所在大气环境[[风切变|风切变]]少，令系统得以发展，同时还受到弱转向气流带动<ref name="BonnieTCR1" />。由于风切变少，风暴[[快速增强|快速增强]]，于18日上午形成尺寸较小但层次分明的[[风眼|风眼]]<ref name="Bonnie5">{{cite report | author = Jerry D. Jarrell | date = 1992-09-18 | title = Hurricane Bonnie Discussion Number 5 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303203534/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.005 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.005 | format = TXT | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。当天下午，邦尼在开放海域蜿蜒行进期间升级成飓风<ref name="BonnieTCR1" />，不过增强速度此后开始放缓。此外，气旋还因转向气流缓慢发展而在9月19日略朝东北转向<ref name="Bonnie8">{{cite report | author = Miles B. Lawrence | date = 1992-09-19 | title = Hurricane Bonnie Discussion Number 8 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304001220/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.008 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.008 | format = TXT | accessdate = 2013-02-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。19日早上，邦尼达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]165公里，中心[[气压|气压]]970[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]）强度，达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的二级飓风标准<ref name="BonnieTCR4">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | date = 1992-12-01 | title = Preliminary best track, Hurricane Bonnie, 17-30 September 1992 | accessdate = 2016-10-16 | page = 4 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193901/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992-prelim/bonnie/prelim04.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992-prelim/bonnie/prelim04.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。风暴的总体朝向和强度这天基本保持不变，次日邦尼虽略有减弱，风眼清晰度降低，但依然维持在二级飓风标准。9月21日清晨，继续缓慢向东北前进的邦尼又略有增强，风眼重新转为清晰<ref name="BonnieTCR1" />。当天下午，气旋逐渐增强，达到持续风速每小时175公里，中心气压965毫巴（百帕，28.5[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度，仅略低于三级飓风标准。邦尼在最高强度下从9月21日夜间保持到9月22日清晨，然后开始以非常稳定的速度减弱。<ref name="BonnieTCR4" />风暴此时开始略向东面转向，但不久又被中纬度[[高压脊|高压脊]]阻挡而基本停止移动<ref name="Bonnie18">{{cite report | author = Harold B. Gerrish | date = 1992-09-22 | title = Hurricane Bonnie Discussion Number 18 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-17 | format = TXT | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222854/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.018 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.018 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

飓风一度停止前进，直到9月23日才开始因高压脊影响而以非常缓慢的速度向西南偏西飘移。同时气旋逐渐减弱，下层中心暴露在外，组织结构变得混乱<ref name="BonnieTCR1" />。对流逐渐消亡，邦尼因行经洋面水温降低而在9月24日下午降级成热带风暴<ref name="Bonnie28">{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | date = 1992-09-24 | title = Tropical Storm Bonnie Discussion Number 28 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192450/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.028 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.028 | format = TXT | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。9月25日，风暴转向南下，其中大部分深层对流逐渐消散，当晚又降级成热带低气压<ref name="BonnieTCR1" />。

风暴的减弱趋势在9月26日清晨中止，邦尼于当天下午重新发展出足够的深层对流，再次达到热带风暴强度<ref name="Bonnie36">{{cite report | author = Jerry D. Jarrell | date = 1992-09-26 | title = Tropical Storm Bonnie Discussion Number 36 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-17 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002358/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.036 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.036 | format = TXT | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋继续改变移动方向，此时转向东南，同时虽受强烈风切变的不利影响，但仍在缓慢发展<ref name="Bonnie38">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | date = 1992-09-27 | title = Tropical Storm Bonnie Discussion Number 38 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303173921/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.038 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.038 | format = TXT }}</ref>。9月27日，正处弱热带风暴强度的邦尼转向东北并表现出转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]的迹象，气象机构在当时的实际操作中宣布风暴已成为温带气旋，直到9月28日下午又改称邦尼此时仍属热带气旋<ref name="Bonnie40">{{cite report | author = Harold B. Gerrish | date = 1992-09-28 | title = Tropical Storm Bonnie Discussion Number 40 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-17 | format = TXT | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193316/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.040 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.040 }}</ref>。在此期间，风暴实际上有所增强，接近热带风暴强度上限<ref name="BonnieTCR4" />。此后气旋总体逼亚速尔群岛逼近，路径与同年的飓风查利基本相同。由于所在环境风切变增多，风暴受到侵蚀，<ref name="Bonnie45">{{cite report | author = Harold B. Gerrish | date = 1992-09-29 | title = Tropical Storm Bonnie Discussion Number 45 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-17 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193459/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.045 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992/bonnie/tropdisc/nal0592.045 | format = TXT | deadurl = no }}</ref>但29日当天邦尼的强度降幅很小，同时加速向东北前进<ref name="BonnieTCR4" />。9月30日，风暴以风力时速100公里的强热带风暴标准经过亚速尔群岛。气旋此后迅速失去热带天气系统特征，于当天下午在亚速尔群岛以东近海转变成温带气旋。<ref name="BonnieTCR1" />残留温带低气压区以顺时针方向回转西南，再度逼近亚速尔群岛并逐渐消亡，最终于10月2日完全消散<ref name="BonnieTCR2">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | date = 1992-10-01 | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Bonnie 17-30 September 1992 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-17 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | page = 2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170259/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992-prelim/bonnie/prelim02.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1992-prelim/bonnie/prelim02.gif }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
邦尼在查利过去仅四天后从亚速尔群岛经过，群岛各地风力普遍达到热带风暴强度。[[拉日什航空基地|拉日什航空基地]]测得的持续风速为每小时64公里，阵风时速94公里。<ref name="BonnieTCR2" />[[圣米格尔岛|圣米格尔岛]]有一人被落石砸死<ref name="mwr">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1992.pdf | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1992 | author1 = B. Max Mayfield | author2 = Lixion A. Avila | author3 = Edward N. Rappaport | date = 1994-03 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-17 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303211604/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1992.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。没有报导表明这场风暴对亚速尔群岛构成任何破坏<ref name="BonnieTCR2" />。

